{
  "texts": [
    "The brain is primarily composed of a large language model, which is the core of an AI agent.",
    "To better explain threats in the brain module, we first show the traditional structure of the brain.",
    "Knowledge Essentials 3.2: The Brain StructureReasoning: Reasoning is a capability based on large language models, similar to human cognitive abilities.",
    "Large language models receive user input as their tasks and decompose these tasks into various subtasks for output.",
    "The ultimate goal is to guide the action module in executing these subtasks."
  ]
}